            "text": "The model handles multilingual documents out-of-the-box, including English, Spanish, French, German, and Chinese, with high accuracy on printed text. It also supports handwritten text recognition for select languages, though performance varies based on legibility. For formats, Nanonets OCR S processes images up to 20MB and PDFs with multiple pages, returning JSON responses with bounding boxes and confidence scores."
