      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For production, log all API responses and set up alerts for anomalies. If accuracy drops, consider fine-tuning Nanonets OCR S with your dataset, though this requires additional effort. OpenAI offers fine-tuning as well, but it's more resource-intensive. Always maintain a fallback mechanism, such as queuing requests during outages."
          }
